Package com.sinch.xms.api

Class MoSms

java.lang.Object
com.sinch.xms.api.MoSms
Direct Known Subclasses:
MoBinarySms, MoTextSms
public abstract class MoSms
extends Object
Base class for mobile originated messages. A mobile originated message can have either a textual or a binary message payload.
